udpcast — NOTICE

clustr-serverd bundles two binaries from the udpcast project:

  udp-sender  (installed at /usr/bin/udp-sender)
  udp-receiver (bundled in the clustr initramfs at /usr/bin/udp-receiver)

These binaries are used for fleet-reimage multicast image delivery
(clustr Sprint 25 #157). They are NOT part of the clustr source code.

